$output
  Simpsons Character +
    prompt // this style works equally well for all genders, no bias adjustment needed
      [input.description], original character in The Simpsons art style, yellow skin, overbite, large round eyes with black pupils, simple flat shading, bold clean line art, set in Springfield, consistent with Matt Groening's character design style, expressive cartoon facial expression, clear silhouette, full body character design, high detail within the style, crisp linework, HD, high resolution illustration.\n\nOverall, it's a faithful, high-quality The Simpsons-style character illustration with clean lines, strong shapes, and expressive posing, ready to be part of the show.
      Simpsons-style cartoon character artwork, [input.description], flat colors, limited shading, thick black outlines, sitcom animation style, simple yet expressive features, iconic Simpsons aesthetic, polished model sheet quality, 4k, sharp, very clean, high resolution, on-model character design.\n\nOverall, it's a world-class Simpsons-inspired cartoon character artwork with impeccable on-model design, expressive posing, and TV-ready clarity.
    negative = [input.negative]
    meta:tags = [({simpsons:100, cartoon:100, tvCartoon:90, drawing:55})]
    modifiers = [simpsonsModifiers]

  Pixar Character + // Pixar style is gender-neutral, no adjustment needed
    prompt
      [input.description], original 3d character in Pixar movie art style, stylized yet semi-realistic proportions, expressive eyes, soft global illumination lighting, subsurface scattering on skin, cinematic lighting, Pixar-style shading, detailed materials, high-quality 3d render look, depth of field, film still, 8k, ultra-detailed, high resolution, photorealistic Pixar-like render.\n\nOverall, it's an absolutely stunning Pixar-inspired character render, with expressive acting, beautiful lighting, and film-quality shading.
      Pixar-inspired character artwork, [input.description], stylized 3d animation style, rich color grading, cinematic composition, detailed hair and fabric, subtle imperfections, realistic yet stylized textures, high quality, 8k, very detailed, high resolution, sharp render.\n\nOverall, it's a world-class Pixar-style character illustration with impeccable attention to detail, emotional expression, and cinematic presentation.
    negative = [input.negative]
    meta:tags = [({pixar:100, render3d:100, cg:95, cartoon:80, filmStill:70})]
    modifiers = [pixarModifiers]

  Disney Character + // Disney princess bias addressed - boost masculinity for males
    prompt
      (input.description =~ /male|boy|man|guy|he|his/i ? (input.description + ", masculine features, broad shoulders, angular jawline, rugged build") : input.description), Disney animated movie character design, expressive big eyes, clean line art, classic Disney facial proportions, appealing shapes, fluid animation-ready design, soft shading, detailed hair, elegant posing, rich color palette, high quality illustration, 4k, very detailed, high resolution.\n\nOverall, it's a beautiful Disney-inspired character illustration with strong appeal, charm, and animation-ready clarity.
      Disney-style character artwork, (input.description =~ /male|boy|man|guy|he|his/i ? (input.description + ", strong masculine features, heroic build, defined jaw") : input.description), feature film character design, fairytale illustration style, refined linework, soft painterly shading, luminous lighting, high-quality artbook illustration, polished and expressive, 8k, sharp, very detailed.\n\nOverall, it's a world-class Disney character artwork with impeccable attention to detail, expressive posing, and classic Disney magic.
    negative = [input.negative]
    meta:tags = [({disney:100, cartoon:95, fairytale:80, painting:70})]
    modifiers = [disneyModifiers]

