simpsonsModifiers
  style
    Classic = , classic early seasons Simpsons art style
    HD = , modern HD Simpsons art style
    Futurama = , Futurama art style, Matt Groening style
  effect
    toon = , bold black outlines, flat cel shading, vibrant colors
    storyboard = , dynamic storyboard pose, action pose, expressive gesture drawing
    lineup = , character turnaround, front and side views, character lineup style

pixarModifiers
  style
    Toy Story = , Toy Story movie art style
    Inside Out = , Inside Out art style, vibrant stylized Pixar look
    Incredibles = , The Incredibles art style, superhero Pixar style
    Turning Red = , Turning Red art style, modern Pixar teen style
  effect
    cinematic = , cinematic lighting, volumetric lighting, filmic color grading, shallow depth of field
    clay = , clay-like shader, soft sculpted forms, plasticine feel
    concept = , character concept sheet, multiple facial expressions, turnaround views

disneyModifiers
  style
    Classic 2D = , classic 2D Disney animation style, hand-drawn look
    Modern 3D = , modern 3D Disney movie style, Tangled/Frozen style
    Renaissance = , 90s Disney Renaissance style, Beauty and the Beast / Aladdin art style
  effect
    storybook = , illustrated storybook style, textured paper, soft watercolor feel
    musical = , dynamic singing pose, dramatic stage lighting, sparkling atmosphere
    royal = , regal composition, ornate costume details, golden lighting

cartoonModifiers
  style
    Western = , Western TV cartoon style, thick outlines, simple shapes
    Minimal = , minimalist cartoon style, very simple shapes, graphic design
    Detailed = , more detailed cartoon style, intricate costume, refined shading
  effect
    lineup = , character turnaround, front and side views, expression sheet
    toon = , bold black outlines, flat cel shading, saturated colors
    dynamic = , action pose, motion lines, dynamic perspective

gameCharacterModifiers
  style
    JRPG = , JRPG character design style, anime-inspired game art
    Western RPG = , Western RPG gritty detailed style, realistic proportions
    FPS Hero = , shooter game hero style, tactical gear, realistic materials
    Platformer = , stylized platformer character, cute simplified shapes
  effect
    splash = , game splash art, dramatic lighting, dynamic composition
    turnaround = , character turnaround sheet, front side and back views
    UI Portrait = , in-game portrait, bust-up framing, clean background

comicModifiers
  style
    American = , American superhero comic style, bold inks, muscular anatomy
    Indie = , indie comic style, loose linework, experimental composition
    Manga = , manga-style comic art, black and white, screentones
  effect
    cover = , comic book cover art, logo space, dramatic centered composition
    panel = , comic panel layout, multiple frames, sequential art
    noir = , noir lighting, high contrast, heavy shadows

pokemonModifiers
  style
    Classic = , classic Ken Sugimori art style, watercolor-like shading
    Modern = , modern Pokémon game artwork style, cleaner digital shading
    Chibi = , chibi style trainer, super-deformed proportions
  effect
    dex = , Pokédex-style entry pose, neutral stance, white background
    battle = , battle pose, dynamic action, speed lines
    team = , trainer with team lineup, multiple creatures

marvelModifiers
  style
    Classic = , classic Silver/Bronze Age Marvel comic style, halftone dots
    Cinematic = , Marvel Cinematic Universe inspired, realistic materials and lighting
    Modern = , modern Marvel comic style, sleek digital coloring
  effect
    cover = , variant cover style, bold logo area, dramatic centered composition
    team = , team lineup, multiple heroes, group pose
    versus = , versus composition, two characters clashing, dynamic diagonal layout

dcModifiers
  style
    Classic = , classic DC comic style, flat coloring, halftone printing feel
    Modern Gritty = , modern gritty DC style, realistic rendering, dark palette
    Animated = , DC animated series style, Bruce Timm / DCAU style
  effect
    cover = , iconic cover art framing, logo space, dramatic lighting
    skyline = , perched on rooftop, city skyline background, moonlit night
    versus = , hero vs villain confrontation, powerful diagonal composition

animeModifiers
  style
    Ghibli = , Ghibli art style, Spirited Away art style
    Your Name = , Your Name / Makoto Shinkai art style
    Paprika = , Paprika art style, Satoshi Kon style
    My Hero Academia = , My Hero Academia art style
    Hunter x Hunter = , Hunter x Hunter art style
    Attack on Titan = , Attack on Titan art style
    KyoAni = , Kyoto Animation art style, soft gradients, detailed eyes
    Trigger = , Studio Trigger art style, bold shapes, extreme expressions
  effect
    multi-view = , multiple views, character turnaround, front and back
    toon = , cartoon-style bold line work, vibrant colors, cel shading
    vintage = , vintage 90s anime style, film grain, muted colors
    ethereal = , glow, god rays, ethereal, dreamy, heavenly, otherworldly, breathtaking, captivating, divine
